20:09.284 --> 20:11.817
You know me so well.

20:11.819 --> 20:13.453
So, recap.

20:13.455 --> 20:14.704
How'd your dinner go?

20:14.706 --> 20:15.955
Oh, pretty well, actually.

20:15.957 --> 20:17.757
The grandmas were
on their best behavior,

20:17.759 --> 20:19.876
and the two boys--
well, let's just say,

20:19.878 --> 20:23.513
