for a long, long time. And you?

20:23.515 --> 20:25.598
Oh, good, good.
It went really good.

20:25.600 --> 20:28.017
So, everything's okay with Zoey?
Yeah, it's fantastic.

20:28.019 --> 20:30.686
Sounds like everything's great
with you and Lyndsey, huh?

20:30.688 --> 20:32.305
Oh, yeah, more than good.

20:32.307 --> 20:34.474
Oh, forgot the honey.

20:36.477 --> 20:38.444
She owns her own home, right?

